            <bug_when>2012-01-04 15:31:46 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>We should use the option to have .po files without occurrences comments, both 
in the framework and all our apps. This type of comment doesn&#39;t bring much 
advantages in our environment, but creates a lot of noise in commit diffs, as 
the line numbers change much more often than the translated keys.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
          <long_desc isprivate="0">
            <commentid>28176</commentid>
            <who name="Thomas Herchenroeder">thron7</who>
            <bug_when>2012-01-04 17:13:09 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>Fixed in most of our apps/components by adding

    &quot;translation&quot; :
    {
      &quot;translate&quot; : { &quot;poentry-with-occurrences&quot; : false  }
    }

in the config (as the default for this config key is currently &#39;true&#39;).

master:167f26f  (last commit of several)</thetext>
